Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:26.48,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I’ve forgotten why I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.94,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I’ve cried in my voracious chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:34.19,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can’t even remember the color of your skin anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:36.84,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Certain that I’m the only one who got hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.48,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I think “whose fault is this, really!?”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.80,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Without even noticing my legs giving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.96,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What about my hopes and dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:49.56,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Was this who I wanted to become?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.10,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The past is just waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:54.90,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Eagerly, with a greedy smile, it waits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:56.94,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If it weren’t for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:00.10,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That loneliness and sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:02.54,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wouldn’t have sung
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.19,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Every time the night died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.26,0:01:07.61,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If your smile had been here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:10.35,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then I never would have given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:12.82,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Remembering your words was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:15.48,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I didn’t need more comforting than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:18.02,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can think of nothing but the meaning of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:20.52,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And so I doubt any sign of kindness, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:23.15,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I realize now now what a shameless person I would’ve been,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:25.69,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If I had laughed at your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:27.98,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As the Uguisu sang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:30.65,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The graduation certificate I tore to pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:33.12,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Fluttered and danced across the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.85,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I’ve devoured the past until nothing remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:02:01.19,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Children, shunned for rebelling, are out for revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:06.21,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}While cowardly adults that cling to their meaning are eager to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:09.35,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The violent thirst for youth idly slumbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:11.94,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}By the time they realize, their nails will be peeling off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:14.47,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I’ve completely forgotten my favorite songs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:17.15,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Or the reason I loved the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:19.58,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The only thing that moves my heart now are things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:22.19,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But even so, I can’t help but long for company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:25.94,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My feelings for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:28.06,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Are the only thing that still lingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:40.02,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Say we happened to meet somewhere by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:42.60,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If I could spin a dream-like story,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:43.85,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then maybe you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:45.57,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Would be able to laugh together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.40,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But if we met through the screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:53.16,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We’d think back on it with only regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.48,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But still, I think back fondly on our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.15,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish we could return there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.54,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If I had been this mature and patient back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.15,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then I’d never have had to experience this pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.73,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If words could have resolved everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.44,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then I wouldn’t have cried so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.94,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I still hated those mornings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:13.40,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because of how you swirled in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.98,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Becoming an adult felt scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.65,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Growing up felt scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.60,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As the Uguisu cries
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.60,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The ragged school uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:26.15,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Fluttered away into the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.90,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I’ve devoured the past until nothing remained.
